From: Nils Toularastel <nils@toularastel.bzh>
Date: Mon, 19 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] drm/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0: disable GFXOFF around GFX/compute ring use

On Navi 48 (RDNA4), GFX and compute ring submissions time out after 60s
when the GPU is in DS_GFXCLK or GFXOFF:

  amdgpu: ring gfx_0.0.0 timeout, signaled seq=N, emitted seq=N+2
  Process kwin_wayland / cs2 VKRenderThread / vkd3d_queue

Triggered when GPU idles (SCLK 0-60 MHz, Load 0-1%) then receives a ring
submission. GPU does not exit DS_GFXCLK before the 60s watchdog fires.

Unlike RDNA2/3 (gfx_v10_0/v11_0), which auto-exit GFXOFF on doorbell,
Navi 48 PMFW requires explicit GFXOFF disable before a doorbell write
is guaranteed to be processed.

gfx_v12_0_ring_begin_use() already exists for power profile and GFX
isolation purposes. Add explicit amdgpu_gfx_off_ctrl(false/true) calls
to disallow GFXOFF while the GFX or compute ring is in use, matching
the fix applied to sdma_v7_0 (patch 1/2) and the existing precedent
in sdma_v5_2.

Cc: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Cc: Christian König <christian.koenig@amd.com>
Link: https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/drm/amd/-/issues/5294
Signed-off-by: Nils Toularastel <nils@toularastel.bzh>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c
index XXXXXXX..YYYYYYY 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/gfx_v12_0.c
@@ -5471,9 +5471,13 @@ static const struct amd_ip_funcs gfx_v12_0_ip_funcs = {

 static void gfx_v12_0_ring_begin_use(struct amdgpu_ring *ring)
 {
+	/* Prevent GFXOFF/DS_GFXCLK: RDNA4 PMFW does not auto-exit on doorbell */
+	amdgpu_gfx_off_ctrl(ring->adev, false);
+
 	amdgpu_gfx_profile_ring_begin_use(ring);
-
 	amdgpu_gfx_enforce_isolation_ring_begin_use(ring);
 }

 static void gfx_v12_0_ring_end_use(struct amdgpu_ring *ring)
 {
 	amdgpu_gfx_profile_ring_end_use(ring);
-
 	amdgpu_gfx_enforce_isolation_ring_end_use(ring);
+
+	amdgpu_gfx_off_ctrl(ring->adev, true);
 }
